The paper deals with query recommendation for a commercial image search engine, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and machine learning for language-related tasks. The paper also uses sequence-to-sequence models, which are commonly used in machine translation (cs.CL) and text summarization (cs.IR). The use of image captions suggests that the paper may also belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) category, which deals with image analysis and recognition. The paper also uses multitask learning, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
